==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Paster
<hw>Past"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
pastes; <as>as, a <ex>paster</ex> in a government
department</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A slip of paper, usually bearing a name, intended to
be pasted by the voter, as a substitute, over another name on a printed
ballot.</def> <mark>[Cant, U.S.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pastern</ent>⟦br⟧
